  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0ddd 20 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Up to 20 youths who allegedly set fire to the Prime Minister's house are remanded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage ordered today 10 to remand three youths arrested by the Kollupitiya Police in connection with the burning of Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe's private house until the 20th for an identification parade.",
        "Three youths between the ages of 28 and 19 residing in Jaela, Galle and Galkissa areas were remanded in custody.",
        "The Kollupitiya Police presented the facts to the court that the Inspector General of Police was instructed to hand over all investigations related to this incident to the custody of the Criminal Investigation Department.",
        "Kollupitiya Police informed the court that these suspects were arrested on the basis of CCTV footage and statements of eyewitnesses related to the incident.",
        "Accordingly, the Kollupitiya police requested the court to remand the suspects to present them in an identification parade as the witnesses want to identify the suspects in the incident.",
        "The lawyers who appeared in court on behalf of the suspects stated that their three clients were innocent in this incident.",
        "Taking into account the facts presented, the magistrate ordered the prison to present the suspects for an identification gate on the 20th and remanded the three until that day."
      ],
